CATEGORY=Special Ability|Magelord ~ Sneak Attack.MOD			DESC:Beginning at 1st level, Magelords deal extra damage (+%1d6) when flanking an opponent or any time a target would be denied its Dexterity bonus. This extra damage applies to ranged attacks only if the target is within 30 feet.|MagelordSneakAttackBonus
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Magelord ~ Magelord Mastered Spell.MOD	DESC:When attaining 2nd level, Magelords can select a spell they already know that they can then prepare without referring to a spellbook, as if they had chosen to master it with the Spell Mastery feat. Magelords can choose another known spell to master in this manner at 4th, 6th, and 8th level.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Magelord ~ Signature Supremacy.MOD		DESC:By 3rd level, Magelords become so familiar with their mastered spells that they can convert any 4th-level or lower prepared spell into any 4th-level or lower mastered spell. Upon attaining 7th level they can convert any 9th-level or lower prepared spell into a 9th-level or lower mastered spell in the same manner.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Magelord ~ Magelord Mastery.MOD		DESC:Finally at 10th level, a Magelord can apply one or more metamagic feats they know to a prepared spell that they have converted into a mastered spell. The level of the prepared spell to be converted must equal or exceed that of the mastered spell with the desired metamagic feats applied.


